params.name: data.model
params.description: Model to use for face detection. Supported values: "builtin/stable" (the default if unset) and "builtin/latest".

params.name: data.include_bounding_boxes
params.description: Whether bounding boxes are included in the face annotation output.

params.name: data.include_attributes
params.description: Whether to enable face attributes detection, such as glasses, dark_glasses, mouth_open etc. Ignored if 'include_bounding_boxes' is set to false.
